text_lines.line_text: Overall pre-sell efforts were successful. Retall accounts that previously stocked
Style Full Price accepted the introduction of the low price.
Proved to be an excellent tool for pulling the balance of Style Full Price packs through
the system. This aided the field greatly during the transition.
Effective in those retail calls that we could not exchange product out of.
